\itemize{
\item \strong{Meta-analysis:} Shrink study-specific effects
\item \strong{Clinical trials:} Borrow information across subgroups or historical controls
\item \strong{Genomics:} Regularize gene-specific effects
\item \strong{Simulation studies:} Compare shrinkage methods systematically
}
